  (A : StarSubalgebra ð•œ C(X, ð•œ)) (hA : Subalgebra.SeparatesPoints A.toSubalgebra) :
  StarSubalgebra.topologicalClosure A = âŠ¤
\end{minted}

We also need (as proved in the last project):

